cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

This paper deals with facial aging and face recognition, which are primarily computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) topics. The paper proposes a novel generative probabilistic model, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also evaluates its approach on various face aging databases, which involves multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
